name: Frozen Wave Orig Painting !!
description:
<object width="500" height="385"><param name="movie" value="//www.youtube.com/v/H9lrwCTTEPA?hl=en_US&version=3&rel=0"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="//www.youtube.com/v/H9lrwCTTEPA?hl=en_US&version=3&rel=0" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="420" height="315" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object>

Frozen Wave Orig Painting !! 36x48

Inspired from Surfing Monterey Bay !!

Painted in less then 35mins with Montana Gold.....Shake rattle and Roll !!!! Painting waves with the rattle can to show respect to the most powerful thing that happens on Earth.....Yet its one of, if not the best thing that is powered by a Tremendous Force that God has Made !! The Ocean is unforgiving but also Full filling.....In my opinion Riding waves is the feeling of how powerful God really is..........Since I fear the Power of God and sometimes Waves he provides us........I feel overwhelmed to Paint them to show my Respect for both Beautiful things !!
